settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
  Template: Press & Media
  This page highlights Trezon's media coverage, press releases, and collaborations.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="press-container">
  <div class="press-banner">
    <h1>Press & Media</h1>
    <p>Discover how Trezon is making waves in the fashion industry.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="press-content">
    <div class="press-section">
      <h2>Featured In</h2>
      <p>We are honored to be featured in leading fashion and lifestyle magazines. Here are some of the publications that have covered Trezon.</p>
      <ul class="press-logos">
        <li><img src="{{ 'press-logo1.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Magazine 1"></li>
        <li><img src="{{ 'press-logo2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Magazine 2"></li>
        <li><img src="{{ 'press-logo3.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Magazine 3"></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="press-section">
      <h2>Press Releases</h2>
      <p>Stay updated with our latest announcements and brand innovations.</p>
      <ul class="press-list">
        <li><a href="/files/press-release-1.pdf" target="_blank">Trezon's New Sustainable Collection â€“ [Date]</a></li>
        <li><a href="/files/press-release-2.pdf" target="_blank">Expanding Our Global Presence â€“ [Date]</a></li>
        <li><a href="/files/press-release-3.pdf" target="_blank">A New Era of Luxury Fashion â€“ [Date]</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="press-section">
      <h2>Brand Collaborations</h2>
      <p>We love working with like-minded brands that share our vision for luxury and sustainability. Explore our collaborations.</p>
      <ul class="collaboration-logos">
        <li><img src="{{ 'brand1-logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Brand 1"></li>
        <li><img src="{{ 'brand2-logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Brand 2"></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="press-section">
      <h2>Media Inquiries</h2>
      <p>For press inquiries, interviews, or collaborations, reach out to us at:</p>
      <p>ðŸ“© Email: <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .press-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background: #EEDFA4; /* Background color */
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .press-banner {
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .press-banner h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #392D00;
  }
  .press-banner p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #5a4300;
  }
  .press-content {
    text-align: left;
  }
  .press-section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .press-section h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #392D00;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .press-section p, .press-list li {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #5a4300;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .press-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .press-list li a {
    color: #392D00;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .press-list li a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .press-logos, .collaboration-logos {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .press-logos img, .collaboration-logos img {
    width: 100px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
</style>
